      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# BiP Devops / Anomaly Detector Benchmark\n\n- Bu dashboard `BiP Devops` klasoru altina import edilmek uzere hazirlandi.\n- Datasource secimi import sirasinda Prometheus olarak yapilmalidir.\n- Panel queryleri, verdigin ham PromQL ifadelerini dogrudan kullanir.\n- Score feed `Auto sync` olarak acik gelir; exporter endpoint varsayilani `http://192.168.51.45:9110`\n- Import sonrasi dashboard kaydedilip anomaly panel kartlarindan score feed rule sync dogrulanmalidir."
      },
      "transparent": false
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "sum(increase(xmpp_messages_total{name=\"O_P2P\"}[5m]))",
